            "subtype": "ability",
            "success": "The creature is unaffected. ",
            "text": "The keribos' heads howl together in a discordant chorus. Every non-keribos within a 30-foot emanation takes 6d6 mental damage and must attempt a DC 21 Will save. After the save, the creature is temporarily immune to all Choruses of Baying for 24 hours.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
